:'''Joanne:''' Huh? Oh, your medical examination was today. My apologies for keeping you waiting.
:'''Joanne:''' There were no appointments listed on the terminal today, so I left for a short break. I wasn't expecting anyone to actually show up.
:'''Joanne:''' Let me see... Well, you're not from the space station, are you? So you were approved by... Oh, lead researcher. These results show several abnormalities...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You have to save me, doctor.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404000217-->
::'''Joanne:''' Don't panic, I'll explain it all to you slowly.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Just give it to me straight, doc. I can take it.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404000219-->
::'''Joanne:''' Okay, I'll cut to the chase.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404000220-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404000220-->
:'''Joanne:''' Have you been feeling drained and lacking motivation to do anything lately? Maybe with some intermittent symptoms like dizziness or tinnitus?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Seems like it, at least a little bit.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404000221-->
::'''Joanne:''' As I expected.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} No, I feel fine.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404000223-->
::'''Joanne:''' Light symptoms such as these can easily go undetected.
:'''Joanne:''' In any case, the situation isn't that grave. To put it bluntly, you're sleep-deprived. You should be more like me, get plenty of rest and don't stay up too late.
:'''Joanne:''' By the way, recently there have been monsters lurking about the space station, so be careful out there. Here're some first aid supplies in case you ever need it. Remember to always clean wounds promptly and thoroughly!
:'''Joanne:''' Don't forget to follow your doctor's orders~
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: 404000202_Finish-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 200030405-->)
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_500216300_436-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_500216300_436-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You are slacking off again?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500216304-->
:::'''Joanne:''' ...What do you mean, slacking off? I'm Joanne from the Medical Department, and I've got a lot to do every day. I need time to relax... otherwise my body won't be able to handle it.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} I heard you didn't rest for a long time?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500216306-->
:::'''Joanne:''' Ooh, don't get me started. I'd been working 24/7 before I burnt out.
:::'''Joanne:''' If you knew this, then just leave me alone. I need to rest...
:::'''Joanne:''' It's worse to disturb someone trying to sleep than wake up someone already asleep.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} So, you got the "memetic virus"?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500216310-->
:::'''Joanne:''' ...Even you are in the know? It must be those blabbermouths at the medical department.
:::'''Joanne:''' Ugh, this is so unfair. I have no idea how I even got this darn thing.
:::'''Joanne:''' Mercifully, it turned out to be a blessing in disguise. I got to take a few days off, and finally got a good night's sleep...
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I better leave you alone then.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500216315-->
:::'''Joanne:''' Sure, you go ahead. I need to get some rest before my next shift.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission not Finish: 200030405-->)
