::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_500010119_1079-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Are you a doctor?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011617-->
:::'''Joanne:''' I'm Joanne, a member of the Medical Department... My scope of work... may be even more complicated than the doctors'.
:::'''Joanne:''' Don't come to me if you are not feeling well. I'm only responsible for the patients under my scope of work. I don't take care of any random people I bump into.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You look sleepy.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011620-->
:::'''Joanne:''' I'm glad you noticed. Stop talking to me then. Disturbing a person who is trying to sleep is even worse than waking up someone who's already asleep.
:::'''Joanne:''' Hey, what's that distrustful and concerned look on your face?
:::'''Joanne:''' Although I easily feel sleepy at work, I take my job very seriously! Don't think of me as some stupid doctor who would leave hemostatic cotton inside their patient!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You look busy.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011624-->
:::'''Joanne:''' I'm glad you noticed. Then leave me alone.
:::'''Joanne:''' I am either delivering or going to deliver medicine. They should've assigned this job to a robot, right?
:::'''Joanne:''' If it wasn't for the Legion's invasion, this kind of thing wouldn't have become my duty.
:::'''Joanne:''' I wish the lead researcher can fix the robot distribution system as soon as possible.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I better leave you alone.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011629-->
:::'''Joanne:''' If you are not feeling well, do not ask for me in the Medical Department. I am very busy.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
